LANG_SPANISH        "^1Harper: ^7Copy that."

REFERENCE           KARMA_VOX_VOX_KAR_12_02_003A_SECT_D
LANG_SPANISH        "^1Section: ^7Harper, heads up.  The Mercs are priming explosives on board."

