LANG_SPANISH        "^1Section: ^7Come on, come on..."

REFERENCE           KARMA_VOX_VOX_KAR_12_02_047A_SECT_D
LANG_SPANISH        "^1Section: ^7Ready?"

REFERENCE           KARMA_VOX_VOX_KAR_12_02_048A_SECT_D
LANG_SPANISH        "^1Section: ^7Go!"

