LANG_SPANISH        "^1Karma: ^7Who the hell are you?!  How'd you know my name?!"

REFERENCE           KARMA_VOX_VOX_KAR_12_02_083A_KARM_S
LANG_SPANISH        "^1Karma: ^7Who are you?!  How'd you know my name?!"

